Selenium Waits
1. Impilcit wait :

All the element applicable - globally apply 
syntax :
driver.manage().timeouts().implicitlyWait(Duration.ofSeconds(10));


2. Explicit wait :

Perticluar element apply --- with condition apply

syntax :
WebDriverWait wait=new WebDriverWait(driver,Duration.ofseconds(5));
wait.until(ExpectedConditions.visibilityofElement(WebELement));

Step :
element action --- weblement show 
elment action --- click enabled

3.Fluent wait : 30 sec --- 5 sec -- check webelement -- ignore exception 
